    What's special

    Completely remodeled 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom ranch on a quiet dead-end street in a great location. Everything has been done—brand new windows, furnace, A/C, hot water tank, and fantastic cosmetic updates. The layout features an open concept main living area with a dedicated dining space and a bright sunroom that brings in tons of natural light. First floor laundry adds everyday convenience, and both bathrooms have been fully updated with modern finishes. The oversized 2-car garage provides plenty of space for parking and storage. Sitting on a quarter-acre lot, the backyard offers a great space to relax, play, or entertain. This home blends modern upgrades with functional design in a peaceful setting—truly move-in ready.
